{"tid":2098660,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"外國跳遠選手質疑港國安法侵犯人權ㅤ籲世界田總禁中國主辦賽事","createTime":"2020-07-07T15:49:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T18:37:24.000Z","uid":105567,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"159e3c10bdefc1cb7c5741c435ea7163e5730901","tid":2098660,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:49:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/0_tqLqT_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F0_tqLqT_1200x0.png&h=9cd42eb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【體路專訊】港區國安法於 6 月 30 日通過並由特區政府公布生效，旋即引來世界各國迴響。外國體壇亦有運動員就此發聲，其中三征奧運的百慕達跳遠運動員 Tyrone Smith 就質疑法例侵犯香港的人權，並呼籲世界田徑總會（World Athletics）禁止中國舉辦鑽石聯賽直至法例被廢除，藉以「在民族尊嚴及經濟上打擊他們」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/sport/%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E8%B7%B3%E9%81%A0%E9%81%B8%E6%89%8B%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E6%B8%AF%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E4%BE%B5%E7%8A%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A-%E7%B1%B2%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%94%B0%E7%B8%BD%E7%A6%81%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%B8%BB%E8%BE%A6%E8%B3%BD%E4%BA%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsport%2F%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25B7%25B3%25E9%2581%25A0%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E7%258A%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A-%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E7%2594%25B0%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%25A6%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E8%25B3%25BD%25E4%25BA%258B%2F&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivcg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=49da0cc8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsport%2F%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25B7%25B3%25E9%2581%25A0%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E7%258A%25AF%25E4%25BA